entries.femaleVariant: Heard even city chooms like to race. Test out their new wheels and all that.
No surprise there. If the car holds out here, it'll hold out anywhere.
Yeah... Anyway, you hear it's just country folks racing, no point even placin' a bet. Anyone's call then.
But if you got a city boy in the mix...
Pure stats. Chances some city gonk fucks up on that route are higher than 'Saka Tower.
Clever. Heard there's some... Bica in the next race? He's from Night City, right?
He is indeed. But he's the exception proves the rule. If Bica's racin', Bica's winnin'. Simple as that.
